import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import torch

from norse.torch.functional.lif_adex import LIFAdExParameters
from norse.torch.functional.lif_adex_refrac import LIFAdExRefracParameters

from tqdm import tqdm
from cgtasknet.net.lifadexrefrac import SNNlifadexrefrac
from cgtasknet.instruments.dynamic_generate import SNNStates
from cgtasknet.instruments.instrument_pca import PCA

from cgtasknet.net.states import LIFAdExRefracInitState
from cgtasknet.tasks.reduce import DefaultParams, RomoTask

dmparams1 = DefaultParams("RomoTask").generate_params()
dmparams1["delay"] = 0.1
dmparams1["trial_time"] = 0.15
dmparams1["values"] = (0.7, 0.9)
Task = RomoTask(dmparams1, mode="value")
dmparams2 = DefaultParams("RomoTask").generate_params()
dmparams2["delay"] = 0.1
dmparams2["trial_time"] = 0.15
dmparams2["values"] = (0.4, 0.8)
Task2 = RomoTask(dmparams2, mode="value")
dmparams3 = DefaultParams("RomoTask").generate_params()
dmparams3["delay"] = 0.1
dmparams3["trial_time"] = 0.15
dmparams3["values"] = (0.4, 0.1)
Task3 = RomoTask(dmparams3, mode="value")
dmparams4 = DefaultParams("RomoTask").generate_params()
dmparams4["delay"] = 0.1
dmparams4["trial_time"] = 0.15
dmparams4["values"] = (0.9, 0.3)
Task4 = RomoTask(dmparams4, mode="value")
feature_size = 2
output_size = 3
hidden_size = 250
batch_size = 1
neuron_parameters = LIFAdExRefracParameters(
    LIFAdExParameters(
        v_th=torch.as_tensor(0.65),
        tau_ada_inv = torch.as_tensor(1),
    ),
    rho_reset=torch.as_tensor(0.5),
)
model = SNNlifadexrefrac(
    feature_size,
    hidden_size,
    output_size,
    neuron_parameters=neuron_parameters,
    tau_filter_inv=500,
    save_states = True,
)
if True:
    model.load_state_dict(
        torch.load("..\models\\only_romo_lif_adex_refrac\\Only_romo_lif_adex_refrac_net_250")
    )
init_state = LIFAdExRefracInitState(batch_size, hidden_size)
first_state = init_state.zero_state()
second_state = init_state.random_state()
inputs, target_out = Task.dataset(1)
one_trajectory_time = inputs.shape[0] * 4   # - 2 + 1500 + 1500
v_mean = torch.zeros((one_trajectory_time,  hidden_size  ))
number_of_trials = 1
#states_generator = SNNStates(model)
for trial in tqdm(range(number_of_trials)):
    inputs, target_out = Task.dataset(1)

    data = inputs  # + np.random.normal(0, 0.01, size=(inputs.shape))
    inputs2, target_out2 = Task2.dataset(1)
    data2 = inputs2  # + np.random.normal(0, 0.01, size=(inputs2.shape))
    data = np.concatenate((data, data2), axis=0)
    inputs3, target_out3 = Task3.dataset(1)
    data3=inputs3
    #data = np.concatenate((data, np.zeros((500, data.shape[1], data.shape[2]))), axis=0)
    data = np.concatenate((data, data3), axis=0)
    inputs4, target_out4 = Task4.dataset(1)
    data4=inputs4
    #data = np.concatenate((data, np.zeros((500, data.shape[1], data.shape[2]))), axis=0)
    data = np.concatenate((data, data4), axis=0)

    #data = np.concatenate((data, np.zeros((500, 1, 2))), axis=0)
    data = torch.from_numpy(data).type(torch.float32)

    out, states = model(data, None)
    v = []
    s = []
    i = []
    a = []
    for j in range(len(states)):
        v.append(states[j].lif_adex.v)
        s.append(states[j].lif_adex.z)
        i.append(states[j].lif_adex.i)
        a.append(states[j].lif_adex.a)

    s = torch.stack(s).detach()
    v = torch.stack(v).detach()
    a = torch.stack(a).detach()
    #v_mean[:, 0, :hidden_size] += v
    v_mean[:, :] += a
v_mean /= float(number_of_trials)
pca = PCA(3).decompose(v_mean.reshape(v_mean.shape[0], v_mean.shape[1]))
cmap = np.arange(0, len(v_mean))


%matplotlib widget
zeros_array = np.zeros((0, 1, 3))
plt.figure()
plt.plot(out[:, 0, :].detach().cpu().numpy()[:, 1])
plt.plot(out[:, 0, :].detach().cpu().numpy()[:, 2])
target_out_all = np.concatenate((target_out, zeros_array, target_out2,zeros_array, target_out3, zeros_array, target_out4))
plt.plot(target_out_all[:, 0, 1])
plt.plot(target_out_all[:, 0, 2])
plt.show()

class PlotTimes:
    delay = int(dmparams1['delay'] / dmparams1['dt'])
    trial = int(dmparams1['trial_time'] / dmparams1['dt'])


trial_1_stop_first = PlotTimes.trial
trial_1_start_second = PlotTimes.delay + PlotTimes.trial

trial_2_start_first = trial_1_start_second + PlotTimes.trial + PlotTimes.delay
trial_2_stop_first = trial_2_start_first + PlotTimes.trial
trial_2_start_second = trial_2_stop_first + PlotTimes.delay
trial_2_stop_second = trial_2_start_second + PlotTimes.trial
msize = 15
plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_1_stop_first, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_1_stop_first, second], '*',  markersize = msize, label='Trial: 1 -- first stop')
plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_1_start_second, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_1_start_second, second], '*', markersize = msize,  label='Trial: 1 -- second start')

plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_2_start_first, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_2_start_first, second], '*', markersize = msize,  label='Trial: 2 -- first start')

plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_2_stop_first, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_2_stop_first, second], '*', markersize = msize,  label='Trial: 2 -- first stop')

plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_2_start_second, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_2_start_second, second], '*', markersize = msize,  label='Trial: 2 -- second start')
plt.plot(pca.numpy()[trial_2_stop_second, first], pca.numpy()[
         trial_2_stop_second, second], '*', markersize = msize,  label='Trial: 2 -- second stop')
plt.legend()

        second = 1

        ax2.set_ylim([-0.5, 1.5])
        ax.clear()
        ax2.clear()
        ax3.clear()
        ax4.clear()

        ax.scatter(pca.numpy()[start:i, first], pca.numpy()[start:i, second], pca.numpy()[start:i, third], cmap='jet', c=[j for j in range(i - start)], s=2)
        

        ax2.clear()
        ax2.plot(data.numpy()[:i, 0, 1], c="black")

        ax3.plot(pca.numpy()[start:i, first], c='black')

        ax.set_xlabel('$PC_1$')
        ax.set_ylabel('$PC_2$')
        ax.set_zlabel('$PC_3$')
        ax2.set_xlabel('Time, ms')
        ax2.set_ylabel('Input')
        ax3.set_xlabel('Time, ms')
        ax3.set_ylabel('$PC_1$')
        ax4.set_xlabel('Time, ms')
        ax4.set_ylabel('$PC_3$')

        fig.canvas.draw()
        fig.canvas.flush_events()
        # time.sleep(.001)


# while True:
update()

from norse.torch.module.exp_filter import ExpFilter


class EXPtest(torch.nn.Module):
    def __init__(self):
        super(EXPtest, self).__init__()

        self.f = ExpFilter(1, 1, 500, bias=False)

    def forward(self, x):
        return self.f(x)


data = torch.zeros((10, 1, 1))
data[0, :] = 1
l = EXPtest()
l(data)
